Class EOArrangement

  • java.lang.Object
    • EOArrangement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EOCSVInterface, EOGUIMultiSelectInterface

    public class EOArrangement
extends java.lang.Object
implements EOCSVInterface, EOGUIMultiSelectInterface
    An implementation of an arrangement. An arrangement, contains events and times for when these are happening.

         Returns the arrangement as one or more CSV lines.
